---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Nick Roth" description="Learn more about Nick Roth - Product Manager and AI Engineer">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="avatar mb-8">
          <div class="w-32 rounded-full ring ring-primary ring-offset-base-100 ring-offset-2">
            <img src="/headshot.jpg" alt="Nick Roth" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Me</h1>
        <p class="text-xl opacity-75 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Product Manager and AI Engineer passionate about building innovative solutions 
          at the intersection of technology and user experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          I'm a seasoned product manager and AI engineer with a passion for creating 
          products that make a real difference in people's lives. My career has been 
          focused on bridging the gap between cutting-edge technology and practical, 
          user-centered design.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Experience</h2>
        <p>
          Throughout my career, I've had the opportunity to work on diverse projects 
          ranging from early-stage startups to enterprise-level solutions. I specialize 
          in translating complex technical concepts into actionable product strategies 
          and user-friendly interfaces.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Skills & Expertise</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Product Strategy & Roadmap Development</li>
          <li>AI/ML Product Integration</li>
          <li>User Experience Design</li>
          <li>Agile Development Methodologies</li>
          <li>Data-Driven Decision Making</li>
          <li>Cross-Functional Team Leadership</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          I believe that the best products are born from a deep understanding of user 
          needs combined with thoughtful application of technology. My approach centers 
          on empathy, iteration, and continuous learning.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>